      • asResolvedClass

        public java.lang.Class<?> asResolvedClass()
        Tries to resolve the given FXML element to a Java class. In case resolution is not possible (e.g. due to the fact the class might not be on the classpath), null is returned.
        Returns:
        the resolved class (or null, in case resolution is not possible.
